punch
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:verb
Sense Number:
Definition:to work or drive cattle (espec. or chiefly, bullocks) as a team); (in NZ the term with dairy cows is spank, occas. bang)
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
